<br>
So, looking at the target types I'm guessing you buff pet with this spell then you get rooted, slowed and healed with 160hp per tick for 24 seconds (kinda like mini-torpor) for a total of a self heal of 640hps.<br>
<br>
Sounds awsome to me.<br>
<br>
